name: FILHA DO SOL #2
description:
A series of fragments taken from the visual album "Daughter of the Sun", B.art's debut album.
A rescue of ancestral memory of the black people and a reflection about Afrofuturism in a world marked by coloniality. This jumpsuit was inspired by 
chinese's "facekini", a outfit used do protect their face of the sun. This music video represents the love in a distopic world.
